Hereâ€™s a 15-minute practical coding task specifically designed for vendor/contractual Java Spring Boot developers who will be doing low-level coding, API development, and deployments.

This task is simple enough to complete quickly, but reveals a lot about their actual ability to write clean, working code.

ğŸ§ª 15-Minute Coding Task: â€œUser Management APIâ€
ğŸ“ Problem Statement

